metadata.name: The Crows
metadata.description:
Crows were flying above me. Like a crowd surrounding and hurting me in depression. Like they have once been, and I believe they were the reason.

But, do crows cause bad luck?
Are good and evil certain?
Or each defines another one and makes a loop.

The loop that turns into vertigo inside my head, comes to an end and it begins again for my better understanding of reasons.
